ep of film production trends, and for seeing aftereffects of the temporary weirdness of sound film deeply etched in the basic character of one of our most enduring film genres.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aHorror filmszUnited StatesxHistory and criticism. 0aSound motion picturesxHistory and criticism. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / General.2bisacsh  a20th century american culture.  a20th century american film history.  aamerican culture.  aamerican film history.  aamerican movie history.  aaudience reception.  acinema.  aclassic horror cinema.  adark.  adracula.  aearly sound film.  afilm studies.  afilmmaking.  afrankenstein.  ahollywood cinema.  ahorror genre.  ahorror movies.  aintense.  amodality.  amovie studies.  asound film.  asvengali.  athe hollywood review of 1929.  auncanny theater.  aunited states of america.  auniversal pictures.  avampires.  aventriloquism.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z97831106904220 cprintz978052025121240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052094070340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520940703423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520940703/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY